node.text:
Family I am so excited to share this journey with you all! I can’t believe I wrote my first book!! 🙌🏾 OOHHHH GOD I THANK YOU!🙌🏾. I hope y’all enjoy it and I pray it helps someone who may feel stuck in their temporary season!! Thank you all so much for your love and support!! Click the link in my bio or here for the book and tour information: https://linktr.ee/Tabs1choyce
#tabithabrown #believer #wife #mom #author #writer #actress #iwroteabook #thankful #feedingthesoul
Big thank you to @harpercollins and @williammorrowbooks

node.title: Feeding the Soul, because it’s my business! Link in my bio❤️

node.text:
Family @donnasrecipe didn’t forget about y’all!! As someone who has several different allergies, I know how hard it can be to find certain products😩. So when y’all said “we need the nut free version Tab”, we listened 🙌🏾. Now available for pre-order!! Click link in my bio to order or go to www.donnasrecipe.com 
#donnasrecipe #hairgrowth #allhairtypes #naturalhair #journey #permedhair #itworks

node.title: To my family with nut allergies, @donnasrecipe got you!!!!

node.text:
Family I am so excited to share this journey with you all! I can’t believe I wrote my first book!! 🙌🏾 OOHHHH GOD I THANK YOU!🙌🏾. I hope y’all enjoy it and I pray it helps someone who may feel stuck in their temporary season!! Thank you all so much for your love and support!! Click the link in my bio or here for the book and tour information: https://linktr.ee/Tabs1choyce
#tabithabrown #believer #wife #mom #author #writer #actress #iwroteabook #thankful #feedingthesoul
Big thank you to @harpercollins and @williammorrowbooks
